{"title":"惠安女子","authors":["周所同"],"dates":[{"year":1989,"month":1,"day":20}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"惠安女子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"周所同"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在远离你的地方想象"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你咬着头巾听那笛声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"踝足淌过咸涩的海水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想象那位诗人搁下笔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"垂着深深的忧伤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄昏的情绪漫过来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"掩去我高原上那盏冬夜的小灯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走近你时已近盛夏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的头巾爬满无名的野花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那顶斗笠比太阳大些"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正好忧郁你的眼睛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而黑裤子是海风做的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咸咸的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我想起我的母亲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就这样擦肩而过"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们都没说些什么"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当你俯身亲你孩子小脸的刹那"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仿佛有谁轻轻唤我的乳名"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我才知道沉重的苦难"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为什么总是缀满美丽的花朵"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}